formance\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun, 37, became something of a global laughing stock after her unorthodox routine, including kangaroo hops and imitating a sprinkler, failed to impress the judges at the Games.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5563354559577668e-28, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"a global laughing stock\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"her unorthodox routine\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"kangaroo hops\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprinkler\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her moves were copied on late-night talk shows and her unfashionable green tracksuit was mercilessly parodied online.\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her moves\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"late-night talk shows\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"her unfashionable green tracksuit\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conspiracy theories abounded to explain how the university lecturer had even made it on to the Australia Olympic team.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9995561278395366, \"rank\": 0.0004409398244653542, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conspiracy theories\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"the university lecturer\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn said the intense scrutiny had been \\\"really upsetting\\\", and she had decided to pull the plug on her breakdancing career.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999675062262847, \"rank\": 1.3735906099673153e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the intense scrutiny\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1008}, {\"ngram\": \"the plug\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"her breakdancing career\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not going to compete any more,\\\" she told Australian radio station 2DayFM on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.8695765641927552, \"rank\": 0.1499047132140227, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was going to keep competing for sure, but that seems like a really difficult thing for me to do now.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really difficult thing\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The level of scrutiny that's going to be there.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"The level\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People will be filming it, it will be going online, it's just not going to be the same experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the same experience\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn had previously spoken out against the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred unleashed towards her after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999675062262847, \"rank\": 1.3735906099673153e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all,\\\" she said in a video message after the Games.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my butt\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"a video message\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While many lampooned her performance on social media, Gunn won support from others, including her fellow Australian Olympians and even the country's prime minister.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999675062262847, \"rank\": 1.373