"crap\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you get out there, and you have fun on the dance floor then just own it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2294, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"the dance floor\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun did have the last laugh in September when she was briefly elevated to the top of the World Dance Sport Federation (WDSF) rankings.\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2418, \"end\": 2422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raygun\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"the last laugh\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2339}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2373, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Dance Sport Federation\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The WDSF named her the number one women's breakdancer based on winning the Oceania Championship, one of only a few events held that counted towards the rankings in the run-up to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2439, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WDSF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_DanceSport_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number one women's breakdancer\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"the Oceania Cha